data.description: Excellent Home in the heart of Goose Creek! No HOA! Enjoy the Huge Fenced-in backyard on a quarter acre + lot with Shed, Spacious deck with dual sliding doors leading to it & Entertain under the screened-in covered porch on the deck. Get very comfy in the bright & spacious sunroom. Enjoy the Large kitchen & open living spaces of this home! Mastersuite has 2 nice closets, Vaulted ceiling Plus a jetted jacuzzi tub to relax the day away! Additional bedrooms have enormous closets. Living room has vaulted ceilings &  wood burning fireplace for those few colder days. New HVAC & Ducts replaced late 2022, Roof is Architectural replaced 2012. Plus enjoy the close proximity of the world-class 13 acres ''Central Creek Park!''  Minutes to downtown Summerville & Charleston! Schedule your tour today!Save with the newer solar panels which will be paid off at closing by seller with acceptable offer. Location! Location! Location!
